dct_description_sm: "5149." Sheets 54, 62, and 65-69 of Garfield, N.J. series; sheets 54 and 62: New sheet, Oct. 1923, showing Lodi and Hasbrouck Heights; sheets 65-70: Add'l. sheet, Oct. 1923, showing Carlstadt, Woodridge and Lodi.
